These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, photographer, paramedic
1. the photographer is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the firefighter is on the far right##1
3. the firefighter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Job   | paramedic | photographer | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Pet   | lizard | guinea-pig | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, nigerian, american
1. the nigerian is in an even position##4
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the american is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Nationality   | german | nigerian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different games are played: chess, go, whist
1. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Game   | chess | whist | go |

