.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different games are played: canasta, chess, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing chess is the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Game   | canasta | chess | billiard |

