.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, snake, hedgehog
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Pet   | snake | hedgehog | goat |

 